C Standard Library
Stratify OS

Stratify OS comes pre-installed with the majority of the C Standard library including:

  • <assert.h>
  • <ctype.h>
  • <errno.h>
  • <float.h>
  • <inttypes.h>
  • <iso646.h>
  • <limits.h>
  • <locale.h>
  • <math.h>
  • <setjmp.h>
  • <signal.h>
  • <stdarg.h>
  • <stdbool.h>
  • <stddef.h>
  • <stdint.h>
  • <stdio.h>
  • <stdlib.h>
  • <string.h>
  • <tgmath.h>
  • <time.h>
  • <wchar.h>
  • <wctype.h>

The following C standard library components are not available:

  • <complex.h>
  • <fenv.h>

If you need to familiarize yourself with the details of the C Standard Library, try the Wikipedia page.
